RBM — Russian Translation
=========================

This is a fan-made Russian localization for the Mount & Blade II: Bannerlord mod
Realistic Battle Mod (RBM).

Attribution
-----------
- Realistic Battle Mod (RBM) — original mod by its respective authors. This
  repository contains only Russian-language string files for RBM and no original
  mod assets or code.
- The translation was written from scratch for this project.

Scope of the MIT license (see LICENSE)
