The MIT license applies to the original contributions in this repository: the
build/tagging tooling under `tools/` and the translation strings.

The translated item and UI names are derivative works of RBM and are shared for the
community's benefit. If you are an original author and have concerns about
attribution or distribution, please open an issue.
